2012-02-23 Roland Hieber <rohieb@rohieb.name>
 * v0.9375 = 15/16
 * add NetworkManager support on systems that provide it (i.e. Linux/Unices)
   The tray icon is now updated every time the network status changes.
 * Don't show notification if the status is the same after network was lost

2012-02-21 Roland Hieber <rohieb@rohieb.name>
 * v0.875 = 7/8
 * show notification popups when opening status changes
   To disable this feature, toggle "Show notifications" in the context menu, or
   start the program with the -s or --silent option.
 * update license to GPLv3 or later
 * fix some smaller bugs

